import React, { useRef } from "react"; function Modal() { useEffect(() => { const handleOutsideClick = (e) => { const dialog = document.getElementById('dialog'); if (!dialog.contains(e.target)) { // Qo'shimcha kod: Agar e.target dialog oynasi ichida bo'lmasa, uni yopish // Masalan, modal.current.close(); yoki modal.current.style.display = 'none'; } }; document.addEventListener('click', handleOutsideClick); return () => { document.removeEventListener('click', handleOutsideClick); }; }, []); // []: Effect bir marta faqat komponent tuzilgandan so'ng chaqiriladi return ( <>
); } export default Modal;
